

PERL packages are used in two places in the ESX Server 1.5 product. 
The following information is provided in compliance with the "Artistic License"

1. The mod_perl package is used in unmodified form.
The version number is 1.26.
It can be downloaded from http://perl.apache.org

2. The unmodified Perl package is linked with vmware-serverd.
The version number is 5.00503.
It can be downloaded from http://www.cpan.org.
